version_description:
Returning Kings Version
<br>1. Improvements to the Friends Return event with new King's Gifts, Spirit Pet Rewards, and Update Features. A wealth of gameplay for returning Lords to help anyone making their way back to the game get up to speed as quickly and effortlessly as possible;
<br>2. New talents added to the Pyramid Battles. Upon entering the battlefield, Lords can pick two talents to help them and their teams overcome the opposition;
<br>3. Improvements to the beginner's guide;
<br>4. New Stealthy Substitute event. Complete quests during the event to earn chest rewards which will be sent out the following day;
<br>5. New Gift of the Djinni event. Use Gift Vouchers during the event to claim awesome rewards!
<br>6. Added New King's Trial event. Designed to help new Kingdoms develop quickly;
<br>7. Other improvements and updates

Anniversary Update
<br>1. New Alliance Gifts: Fellow Alliance members will receive gifts when you purchase packs, when eligible;
<br>2. New anniversary events: Anniversary Treasure Hunt, Memory Shards, Goodwill Packs Galore, Happy Anniversary, and more! Brand new anniversary themed decoration set;
<br>3. New events: Reset Buffs, Kingdom's Favor, Feast of Heroes, and Hammer Time;
<br>4. Improvements to existing events: Regal Alliance League and Top Lord (event rules and rewards);
<br>5. Improvements to the Pyramid Battlefield;
<br>6. Other updates and improvements

